title: 25 Self-Improvement Books That Will Make You A Better Person
description:
25 Self-Improvement Books That Will Make You A Better Person

List Of Books Included:

1.Daniel Kanheman - Thinking, Fast and Slow

2.Eckhart Tolle - A New Earth_ Awakening to Your Life's Purpose

3.Augusten Burroughs - This is How

4.Dalai Lama - The Art of Happiness

5.Daniel G. Amen - Change Your Brain, Change Your Life

6.Eckhart Tolle - The Power of Now

7.Emotional Intelligence - Daniel Goleman

8.For Your Own Good - Hidden Cruelty in Child-Rearing and the Roots of Violence - 
Alice Miller

9.Jonathan Haidt - The Happiness Hypothesis_ Finding Modern Truth in Ancient Wisdom

10.Malcolm Gladwell - Outliers_ The Story of Success

11.Man's Search for Meaning - Viktor E. Frankl

12.Maxwell Maltz - Psycho-Cybernetics

13.Spencer Johnson - Who Moved My Cheese__ An Amazing Way to Deal with Change

14.Steven Pinker - The Blank Slate - The Modern Denial of Human Nature

15.Stuart Wilde - Life Was Never Meant to Be a Struggle

16.Susan Jeffers - Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway

17.Switch - How to Change Things When Change Is Hard - Chip Heath, Dan Heath

18.The Attention Revolution - Unlocking the Power of the Focused Mind - B. Alan Wallace

19.The Highly Sensitive Person - Elaine Aron

20.The Now Habit - Neil Fiore

21.The Road Less Traveled - A New Psychology of Love, Traditional Values and Spiritual Growth - M. Scott Peck

22.The Tipping Point - How Little Things Can Make a Big Difference - Malcolm Gladwell

23.The Upside of Irrationality - The Unexpected Benefits of Defying Logic - Dan Ariely

24.Whatcha Gonna Do with That Duck - Seth Godin

25.You Are Not So Smart - David McRaney
